Plan to implement                                                                                                                                                                   │
│                                                                                                                                                                                     │
│ Agentic Churn Prediction Pipeline                                                                                                                                                   │
│                                                                                                                                                                                     │
│ Context                                                                                                                                                                             │
│                                                                                                                                                                                     │
│ The current churn-tool pipeline is linear: upload → column map → hypothesis → features → labels → train → results → inference. It has three problems:                               │
│                                                                                                                                                                                     │
│ 1. Fixed feature catalog — The LLM selects from 22 predefined features (10 Tier 1 + 12 Tier 2). It cannot create new features based on data patterns.                               │
│ 2. Single model, single pass — Only XGBoost is trained. No comparison. No iteration. If the model has data leakage or poor metrics, the pipeline does not self-correct.             │
│ 3. No user interaction after upload — The user answers MCQs once, then waits for results. They cannot correct interpretations, request feature changes, or compare models mid-run.  │
│                                                                                                                                                                                     │
│ This plan converts the pipeline into an agentic loop that: generates features via a DSL, trains multiple models (XGBoost + RF), detects data leakage via LLM, iterates until        │
│ success criteria are met, and exposes a chat interface for user interaction.                                                                                                        │
