│ Component 1: Feature DSL                                                                                                                                                            │
│                                                                                                                                                                                     │
│ Purpose: Let the LLM describe custom features in a structured JSON format. A DSL interpreter converts them to pandas operations.                                                    │
│                                                                                                                                                                                     │
│ File: app/agent/feature_dsl.py                                                                                                                                                      │
│                                                                                                                                                                                     │
│ DSL Operations                                                                                                                                                                      │
│ Operation: aggregate                                                                                                                                                                │
│ Description: Per-customer aggregation                                                                                                                                               │
│ Example: {"op": "aggregate", "column": "amount", "func": "mean"} → avg spend per customer                                                                                           │
│ ────────────────────────────────────────                                                                                                                                            │
│ Operation: aggregate_window                                                                                                                                                         │
│ Description: Aggregation within time window                                                                                                                                         │
│ Example: {"op": "aggregate_window", "column": "amount", "func": "sum", "window_days": 30} → spend in last 30 days                                                                   │
│ ────────────────────────────────────────                                                                                                                                            │
│ Operation: ratio                                                                                                                                                                    │
│ Description: Ratio of two aggregations                                                                                                                                              │
│ Example: {"op": "ratio", "numerator": {"column": "amount", "func": "sum", "window_days": 30}, "denominator": {"column": "amount", "func": "sum"}} → recent spend ratio              │
│ ────────────────────────────────────────                                                                                                                                            │
│ Operation: trend                                                                                                                                                                    │
│ Description: First-half vs second-half comparison                                                                                                                                   │
│ Example: {"op": "trend", "column": "quantity", "func": "mean"} → increasing or decreasing order size                                                                                │
│ ────────────────────────────────────────                                                                                                                                            │
│ Operation: conditional_count                                                                                                                                                        │
│ Description: Count rows matching condition                                                                                                                                          │
│ Example: {"op": "conditional_count", "column": "amount", "condition": "> 50"} → high-value transaction count                                                                        │
│ ────────────────────────────────────────                                                                                                                                            │
│ Operation: nunique                                                                                                                                                                  │
│ Description: Distinct count per customer                                                                                                                                            │
│ Example: {"op": "nunique", "column": "product"} → product diversity                                                                                                                 │
│ ────────────────────────────────────────                                                                                                                                            │
│ Operation: gap_stat                                                                                                                                                                 │
│ Description: Statistic on inter-purchase gaps                                                                                                                                       │
│ Example: {"op": "gap_stat", "func": "max"} → longest gap between purchases                                                                                                          │
│ DSL Schema (Pydantic)                                                                                                                                                               │
│                                                                                                                                                                                     │
│ class DSLFeature(BaseModel):                                                                                                                                                        │
│     name: str                    # e.g. "recent_spend_ratio"                                                                                                                        │
│     description: str             # human-readable explanation                                                                                                                       │
│     operation: str               # one of the DSL operations above                                                                                                                  │
│     params: dict                 # operation-specific parameters                                                                                                                    │
│                                                                                                                                                                                     │
│ LLM Feature Suggestion                                                                                                                                                              │
│                                                                                                                                                                                     │
│ The LLM receives:                                                                                                                                                                   │
│ - Data profile (columns, dtypes, sample values)                                                                                                                                     │
│ - Column mapping                                                                                                                                                                    │
│ - Business hypothesis                                                                                                                                                               │
│ - Features already computed (Tier 1 + Tier 2)                                                                                                                                       │
│ - Current iteration metrics (if iteration > 0)                                                                                                                                      │
│                                                                                                                                                                                     │
│ The LLM outputs a list of DSLFeature objects. The interpreter executes each, appends the result to the feature matrix.                                                              │
│                                                                                                                                                                                     │
│ Pydantic schema: LLMFeatureSuggestionOutput                                                                                                                                         │
│ class LLMFeatureSuggestionOutput(BaseModel):                                                                                                                                        │
│     suggested_features: list[DSLFeature]                                                                                                                                            │
│     reasoning: str                                                                                                                                                                  │
│                                                                                                                                                                                     │
│ Interpreter                                                                                                                                                                         │
│                                                                                                                                                                                     │
│ def execute_dsl_feature(                                                                                                                                                            │
│     df: pd.DataFrame,                                                                                                                                                               │
│     col_map: dict,                                                                                                                                                                  │
│     feature_def: DSLFeature,                                                                                                                                                        │
│ ) -> pd.Series:                                                                                                                                                                     │
│                                                                                                                                                                                     │
│ Returns a Series indexed by customer_id. If execution fails (bad column name, unsupported operation), the feature is skipped and logged.                                            │
│                                                                                                                                                                                     │
