│ Component 3: LLM Evaluator                                                                                                                                                          │
│                                                                                                                                                                                     │
│ File: app/agent/evaluator.py                                                                                                                                                        │
│                                                                                                                                                                                     │
│ Evaluation Prompt                                                                                                                                                                   │
│                                                                                                                                                                                     │
│ After training, the LLM receives:                                                                                                                                                   │
│ - All model results (metrics + feature importance for each)                                                                                                                         │
│ - Feature definitions (what each feature measures)                                                                                                                                  │
│ - Churn label definition (window, cutoff)                                                                                                                                           │
│ - Iteration history (previous iterations' metrics and adjustments)                                                                                                                  │
│                                                                                                                                                                                     │
│ Evaluation Output                                                                                                                                                                   │
│                                                                                                                                                                                     │
│ class LLMEvaluationOutput(BaseModel):                                                                                                                                               │
│     leakage_detected: bool                                                                                                                                                          │
│     suspect_features: list[str]         # features to remove                                                                                                                        │
│     leakage_reasoning: str                                                                                                                                                          │
│     quality_acceptable: bool                                                                                                                                                        │
│     best_model: str                     # "xgboost" or "random_forest"                                                                                                              │
│     suggested_adjustments: list[str]    # ["remove recency", "add feature: ..."]                                                                                                    │
│     reasoning: str                                                                                                                                                                  │
│                                                                                                                                                                                     │
│ Leakage Detection Heuristics (given to LLM as context)                                                                                                                              │
│                                                                                                                                                                                     │
│ The LLM checks:                                                                                                                                                                     │
│ 1. Single feature dominance: One feature > 80% importance                                                                                                                           │
│ 2. Perfect metrics: AUC > 0.99 with any single feature > 50%                                                                                                                        │
│ 3. Tautological features: Feature definition overlaps with label definition (e.g., recency measures "days since last purchase" and churn label means "no purchase in last N days")  │
│                                                                                                                                                                                     │
│ Success Criteria (default, stored in session)                                                                                                                                       │
│                                                                                                                                                                                     │
│ SUCCESS_CRITERIA = {                                                                                                                                                                │
│     "min_auc": 0.7,                                                                                                                                                                 │
│     "min_f1": 0.5,                                                                                                                                                                  │
│     "max_top_feature_importance": 0.80,                                                                                                                                             │
│     "min_features_above_5pct": 3,                                                                                                                                                   │
│ }                                                                                                                                                                                   │
│                                                                                                                                                                                     │
│ The evaluation is a combination of:                                                                                                                                                 │
│ - Rule-based checks against success criteria (hard gates)                                                                                                                           │
│ - LLM judgment on leakage and quality (soft analysis)                                                                                                                               │
│                                                                                                                                                                                     │
│ ---                                                                                                                                                                                 │
│ Component 4: Agent Loop                                                                                                                                                             │
│                                                                                                                                                                                     │
│ File: app/agent/loop.py                                                                                                                                                             │
│                                                                                                                                                                                     │
│ State                                                                                                                                                                               │
│                                                                                                                                                                                     │
│ @dataclass                                                                                                                                                                          │
│ class AgentState:                                                                                                                                                                   │
│     session_id: str                                                                                                                                                                 │
│     iteration: int = 0                                                                                                                                                              │
│     max_iterations: int = 5                                                                                                                                                         │
│     status: str = "running"          # running | success | failed | interrupted                                                                                                     │
│     history: list[IterationResult] = field(default_factory=list)                                                                                                                    │
│     champion: ModelResult | None = None                                                                                                                                             │
│     excluded_features: list[str] = field(default_factory=list)                                                                                                                      │
│     dsl_features: list[DSLFeature] = field(default_factory=list)                                                                                                                    │
│     user_overrides: dict = field(default_factory=dict)                                                                                                                              │
│     success_criteria: dict = field(default_factory=lambda: SUCCESS_CRITERIA.copy())                                                                                                 │
│                                                                                                                                                                                     │
│ @dataclass                                                                                                                                                                          │
│ class IterationResult:                                                                                                                                                              │
│     iteration: int                                                                                                                                                                  │
│     features_used: list[str]                                                                                                                                                        │
│     features_removed: list[str]                                                                                                                                                     │
│     features_added: list[str]                                                                                                                                                       │
│     model_results: list[ModelResult]                                                                                                                                                │
│     evaluation: LLMEvaluationOutput                                                                                                                                                 │
│                                                                                                                                                                                     │
│ Loop Logic                                                                                                                                                                          │
│                                                                                                                                                                                     │
│ async def run_agent(state: AgentState, session: dict) -> AgentState:                                                                                                                │
│     while state.iteration < state.max_iterations:                                                                                                                                   │
│         state.iteration += 1                                                                                                                                                        │
│                                                                                                                                                                                     │
│         # 1. Compute features (Tier 1 + Tier 2 + DSL, excluding banned features)                                                                                                    │
│         feature_matrix = compute_features(session, state)                                                                                                                           │
│                                                                                                                                                                                     │
│         # 2. Compute labels                                                                                                                                                         │
│         labels = compute_labels(session)                                                                                                                                            │
│                                                                                                                                                                                     │
│         # 3. Train all models                                                                                                                                                       │
│         X_train, X_test, y_train, y_test = split(feature_matrix, labels)                                                                                                            │
│         model_results = train_all_models(X_train, X_test, y_train, y_test)                                                                                                          │
│                                                                                                                                                                                     │
│         # 4. Evaluate (LLM + rules)                                                                                                                                                 │
│         evaluation = await evaluate(model_results, state)                                                                                                                           │
│                                                                                                                                                                                     │
│         # 5. Record iteration                                                                                                                                                       │
│         state.history.append(IterationResult(...))                                                                                                                                  │
│                                                                                                                                                                                     │
│         # 6. Stream progress to chat                                                                                                                                                │
│         await broadcast_progress(state)                                                                                                                                             │
│                                                                                                                                                                                     │
│         # 7. Check success                                                                                                                                                          │
│         if evaluation.quality_acceptable and not evaluation.leakage_detected:                                                                                                       │
│             state.champion = select_champion(model_results, evaluation)                                                                                                             │
│             state.status = "success"                                                                                                                                                │
│             break                                                                                                                                                                   │
│                                                                                                                                                                                     │
│         # 8. Apply adjustments                                                                                                                                                      │
│         for feat in evaluation.suspect_features:                                                                                                                                    │
│             state.excluded_features.append(feat)                                                                                                                                    │
│                                                                                                                                                                                     │
│         # 9. Ask LLM for new features if needed                                                                                                                                     │
│         if state.iteration < state.max_iterations:                                                                                                                                  │
│             new_features = await suggest_dsl_features(session, state)                                                                                                               │
│             state.dsl_features.extend(new_features)                                                                                                                                 │
│                                                                                                                                                                                     │
│     if state.status != "success":                                                                                                                                                   │
│         # Pick best model from all iterations                                                                                                                                       │
│         state.champion = pick_best_across_iterations(state.history)                                                                                                                 │
│         state.status = "completed"                                                                                                                                                  │
│                                                                                                                                                                                     │
│     return state                                                                                                                                                                    │
│                                                                                                                                                                                     │
│ User Interruption                                                                                                                                                                   │
│                                                                                                                                                                                     │
│ The agent checks for user overrides between steps 6 and 7:                                                                                                                          │
│ overrides = check_user_overrides(state.session_id)                                                                                                                                  │
│ if overrides:                                                                                                                                                                       │
│     apply_overrides(state, overrides)                                                                                                                                               │
│     # overrides can: add/remove features, change success criteria,                                                                                                                  │
│     # force a specific model, skip to completion                                                                                                                                    │
│                                                                                                                                                                                     │
